      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «اِصْنَعِ اَلْمَعْرُوفَ إِلَى كُلِّ أَحَدٍ فَإِنْ كَانَ أَهْلَهُ وَ إِلاَّ فَأَنْتَ أَهْلُهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1683 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Perform acts of kindness for everyone. If they are deserving of it, then it is for them; and if not, then you are worthy of it.\""
        ]
      }
